BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 509.20 Td (The FPGA/HSB default IP is:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 486.40 Td (192.168.0.2) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 465.40 Td (Configure Thor:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 442.60 Td (EN0=mgbe0_0) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 423.40 Td (sudo nmcli connection delete hololink-$EN0 2>/dev/null || true) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 413.80 Td (sudo nmcli con add con-name hololink-$EN0 ifname $EN0 type ethernet ip4 192.168.0.101/24) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 404.20 Td (sudo nmcli connection modify hololink-$EN0 +ipv4.routes 192.168.0.2/32) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 394.60 Td (sudo nmcli connection up hololink-$EN0) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 373.60 Td (What this does / why required:) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 350.80 Td (- EN0=mgbe0_0 selects the Thor MGBE port connected to the FPGA.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 339.40 Td (- nmcli connection delete removes any stale Hololink profile so the IP setup is clean.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 328.00 Td (- nmcli con add assigns Thor the static host IP 192.168.0.101/24.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 316.60 Td (- +ipv4.routes 192.168.0.2/32 adds a direct route to the FPGA/HSB IP.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 305.20 Td (- connection up activates the interface profile.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 282.40 Td (Test:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 259.60 Td (ping 192.168.0.2) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 238.60 Td (What this does / why required:) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 215.80 Td (- Confirms basic IP reachability to the FPGA.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 204.40 Td (- If this fails with Destination Host Unreachable, debug link/cable/FPGA programming before running) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 193.00 Td (  Holoscan applications.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 170.20 Td (Check link status:) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 147.40 Td (for i in 0 1 2 3; do) Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 137.80 Td (  echo "---- mgbe${i}_0 ----") Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 128.20 Td (  sudo ethtool mgbe${i}_0 | grep -E "Speed|Link detected") Tj ET
BT /F3 7.8 Tf 54 118.60 Td (done) Tj ET
