BT /F2 14 Tf 54 652.60 Td (11. Known Issues and Lessons Learned) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 623.20 Td (- Thor defaults to 10GbE mode.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 611.80 Td (- 25GbE FPGA images need Thor booted in 25GbE mode.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 600.40 Td (- 10G/25G mode switching requires boot slot / capsule handling, not nmcli.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 589.00 Td (- Early MDK boards may need MAX10 reflashing to power MIPI connectors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 577.60 Td (- Camera I2C errors can be caused by missing MIPI connector power, not only cable orientation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 566.20 Td (- hololink-enumerate confirms the FPGA/HSB network path.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 554.80 Td (- GUI failures are often X11 authorization issues.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 543.40 Td (- .sof FPGA programming is volatile; reprogram after FPGA board power cycle.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 532.00 Td (- For customer demos on AGX Thor, 10GbE and Linux socket mode are the most stable paths. 25GbE CoE is) Tj ET
BT /F1 9.0 Tf 54 520.60 Td (  available but may show stability issues under some multi-stream scenarios.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 498 28 Td (Page 9 of 9) Tj ET
endstream
